{"tid":2313682,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"想試下入抗jojo","createTime":"2020-12-06T04:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T16:06:00.000Z","uid":3172,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"da6aa54191df347ddeaa095d5b6bbf594851c458","tid":2313682,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:16:05.000Z","msg":"係咪睇不滅鑽石先最好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf32ab63a5606320f9f633617c3a05a1990f085","tid":2313682,"uid":71913,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:22:54.000Z","msg":"由第一季開始睇 動畫表演力唔差 唔會悶"},{"pid":"a1ece60d3ef773870e800312a3f127f532690586","tid":2313682,"uid":12633,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/caCL1bf70AU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcaCL1bf70AU&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo%2BSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=2ee2bd4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/caCL1bf70AU</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左呢段片你就知"},{"pid":"4f559dba6bbc03bb2a40cd08a2ae0d28084ce6e0","tid":2313682,"uid":11913,"like":48,"dislike":3,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"每當見到有人諗住由中間開始入坑嘅人，我只係有有忠告：<br />\n<br />\n當你睇完愛上jojo之後補返個開頭，你會後悔自己點解當初唔係由第一部開始睇<br />\n<br />\n利申：由第一部開始睇"},{"pid":"90b50c97569db33b52e456b0306d6393c17445e8","tid":2313682,"uid":62040,"like":27,"dislike":7,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T05:16:17.000Z","msg":"我自己係netflix第一季開始睇<br />\n我唔怕老套劇情, 睇第一季覺得係有D老套, 但諗到佢漫畫原作係80年代既作品就覺得好正常, 作畫同節奏都做得好好, 其實老套得黎無咩悶場, 我強烈建議第一季開始<br />\n雖然係第4季開始都無咩問題既, 但係順住睇第一第二季都好撚正<br />\n我個人係麻麻地第3季, 覺得中間旅行嗰part有D太長有D慢, 但亦有好多人好鍾意第三季個主題同埋做法<br />\n最鍾意係 2 &gt; 4 &gt; 1 &gt; 3<br />\n但整體都係好出色, 純粹要排我就咁排"},{"pid":"dc05192ec06f0fca4b976b40155a41e9eec99eca","tid":2313682,"uid":296715,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"da6aa54191df347ddeaa095d5b6bbf594851c458","tid":2313682,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:16:05.000Z","msg":"係咪睇不滅鑽石先最好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T05:57:01.000Z","msg":"動畫的話強烈建議從第一部開始看"},{"pid":"74e5226595f5e774c3515e9a119b058c255aa358","tid":2313682,"uid":2716,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"第3部第4部後半先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第2就成個故事一氣呵成好爽"},{"pid":"db18a8362bf34e60ae4c3e9d9aac77509a6fbd65","tid":2313682,"uid":31572,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"老實講 除咗第一部old school 少少<br />\n其他都正到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7094897af35507ed6c97319a1e53c8cacd7f4b","tid":2313682,"uid":335335,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T06:35:42.000Z","msg":"第一季開始睇啦 一開始畫風可能會頂唔順 但慢慢接受左就會覺得好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffa3f66aad3265a093c08f2860b231bdbfa0b47","tid":2313682,"uid":237415,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T07:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/su0uA0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsu0uA0b.jpg&h=32b02eee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一季開始睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fed72ca888cc644991a22b6bb25e93809e9ea43","tid":2313682,"uid":29689,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:01:29.000Z","msg":"係咪得我最鐘意第一季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得最簡單直接打得又有血有肉<br />\n有左替身之後覺得啲人物角色只係負責出血咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271b39b9817e16a81a31ba7a050e980f71e12d0f","tid":2313682,"uid":277847,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"一定要由第一季開始睇"},{"pid":"85c4d6e61fca51570a75c6d2d965988f58f8289e","tid":2313682,"uid":14423,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:48:18.000Z","msg":"第一季係一開始難捱<br />\n但照睇去儲吓黃金精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6118e71b2a3f694e8b42e9d57fb371f632afdb48","tid":2313682,"uid":288675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:53:27.000Z","msg":"直接睇第三部ova <br />\n反而可補番1 2 當前傳"},{"pid":"b805e6c4e57733b0318700be1517347e61eb7e9a","tid":2313682,"uid":279932,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:54:35.000Z","msg":"動畫接住睇就得<br />\n漫畫skip 第六部，個人覺得最好睇係七部"},{"pid":"68a25cd40fea8e605d599fae13e5f9543614f102","tid":2313682,"uid":219265,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T09:54:57.000Z","msg":"一定要順序睇<br />\n但我自己覺得 2&gt;4&gt;5&gt;1&gt;3係最正"},{"pid":"dc1c00396c31f580cd99e2504849728635a75631","tid":2313682,"uid":248631,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"咩係入抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0810f55705a8c44835949052cefde5caa10d4005","tid":2313682,"uid":134174,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"第一季好多金句，而且難得有角色成長描寫，第二季打後時間跨度好短<br />\n第二季睇二jo食腦戰鬥<br />\n第三季典型公路戲，第四季日常，煲會覺得悶，一日睇一集就好正，去到boss戰直落<br />\n第五季就一個個單元故事，動畫嚟講完成度高，邪道角色邪道戰鬥，風格幾有趣"},{"pid":"df61f6ec94be18d248fe63b23518598819f1c617","tid":2313682,"uid":39188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:11:40.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完jojo動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得開頭到中段多數都係好普通 唔係特別吸引<br />\n但係中段開始 一入boss戰就會好吸引 追住一集一集咁睇落去 完全唔想停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac231da84a496d5327eafec8e855b4cb1282f002","tid":2313682,"uid":189338,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:11:54.000Z","msg":"第一季就好似入學試咁 頂過咗 習慣咗佢嘅畫風 習慣咗佢地會瘋狂說明 之後就季季都好有新鮮感 好正<br />\n<br />\n不得不承認只係討論第一季嘅話睇完係會滿頭問號 有咩咁正呀 瘋狂超展開唔知做緊咩 但睇落去就會明 個奇妙之處 可以嘅話都唔建議skip 由第一季慢慢睇 你當第一季係前傳性質咁睇 當知下個底 睇埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4801882a433ad37793cb8c3df134e364bda14808","tid":2313682,"uid":5320,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"db18a8362bf34e60ae4c3e9d9aac77509a6fbd65","tid":2313682,"uid":31572,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"老實講 除咗第一部old school 少少<br />\n其他都正到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:15:28.000Z","msg":"有Speedwagon已經值得睇第一部"},{"pid":"7ed53c4e3d5d1d4cb1ff71b00ee565a0cba88302","tid":2313682,"uid":4179,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"第一季睇咗5,6集 好悶停咗"},{"pid":"11cdb9c87c191f3b3eb9d8388b16c7376ed2336a","tid":2313682,"uid":305638,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1fed72ca888cc644991a22b6bb25e93809e9ea43","tid":2313682,"uid":29689,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:01:29.000Z","msg":"係咪得我最鐘意第一季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得最簡單直接打得又有血有肉<br />\n有左替身之後覺得啲人物角色只係負責出血咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T09:03:01.000Z","msg":"第一季肯定唔夠之後好睇就一定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我最鐘意第一季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係第一集難頂 <br />\n但正正係呢集帶出左dio點解會係大boss<br />\n<br />\n雖然集數少 但個個人物都好完整 故事節奏又順又快"},{"pid":"76aff38b3d9b7e268767cef18d87d6bc96147f8a","tid":2313682,"uid":102978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"點打解入坑要中間入..<br />\n第1集已經令人追落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78adf788f83ce58489a1b1771a633dcf6fdb3ce6","tid":2313682,"uid":2313,"l